as</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas/tree/kata-data-transformers\">Kata 1: (Form) DataTransformer</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-14T11:26:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"gamontal/awesome-katas","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas\">SensioLabs PoleDev Katas</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas/tree/kata-event-listener\">Kata 2: (EventDispatcher) Event Listener / Event Dispatcher</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-14T11:26:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"gamontal/awesome-katas","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas\">SensioLabs PoleDev Katas</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas/tree/kata-inherit-data\">Kata 3: (Form) Inherit data / Virtual Form</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-14T11:26:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"gamontal/awesome-katas","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas\">SensioLabs PoleDev Katas</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas/tree/kata-upload-file\">Kata 4: (Form) File Upload</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-14T11:26:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"gamontal/awesome-katas","categoryHTML":"<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas\">SensioLabs PoleDev Katas</a></h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/devdrops/Katas/tree/kata-translation\">Kata 5: (Translation) Manage translations</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-07-14T11:26:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rust-unofficial/awesome-rust","categoryHTML":"<h2>Development tools</h2><h3>Build system</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/\">Cargo</a> — the Rust package manager\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-benchcmp\">cargo-benchcmp</a> — A utility to compare Rust micro-benchmarks <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/BurntSushi/cargo-benchcmp\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/BurntSushi/cargo-benchcmp.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-bitbake\">cargo-bitbake</a> — A cargo extension that can generate BitBake recipes utilizing the classes from meta-rust <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/cardoe/cargo-bitbake\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/cardoe/cargo-bitbake.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-cache\">cargo-cache</a> — inspect/manage/clean your cargo cache (<code>~/.cargo/</code>/<code>${CARGO_HOME}</code>), print sizes etc <a href=\"https://github.com/matthiaskrgr/cargo-cache/actions\"><img src=\"https://github.com/matthiaskrgr/cargo-cache/workflows/ci/badge.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"Build Status\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-check\">cargo-check</a> — A wrapper around <code>cargo rustc -- -Zno-trans</code> which can be helpful for running a faster compile if you only need correctness checks <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/rsolomo/cargo-check\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/rsolomo/cargo-check.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-count\">cargo-count</a> — lists source code counts and details about cargo projects, including unsafe statistics <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-count\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-count.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-deb\">cargo-deb</a> — Generates binary Debian packages <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/mmstick/cargo-deb\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/mmstick/cargo-deb.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-deps\">cargo-deps</a> — build dependency graphs of Rust projects <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/m-cat/cargo-deps\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.com/m-cat/cargo-deps.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-do\">cargo-do</a> — run multiple cargo commands in a row <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/pwoolcoc/cargo-do\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/pwoolcoc/cargo-do.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-ebuild\">cargo-ebuild</a> — cargo extension that can generate ebuilds using the in-tree eclasses <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/cardoe/cargo-ebuild\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/cardoe/cargo-ebuild.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-edit\">cargo-edit</a> — allows you to add and list dependencies by reading/writing to your Cargo.toml file from the command line <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/killercup/cargo-edit\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/killercup/cargo-edit.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/cargo-generate/cargo-generate\">cargo-generate</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/cargo-generate/cargo-generate\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">715</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":715,\"repo\":\"cargo-generate/cargo-generate\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> A generator of a rust project by leveraging a pre-existing git repository as a template.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-get\">cargo-get</a> - Cargo plugin to easily query information from Cargo.toml files <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/workflow/status/nicolaiunrein/cargo-get/CI\" alt=\"GitHub Workflow Status\"></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-graph\">cargo-graph</a> — updated fork of <code>cargo-dot</code> with additional features. Unmaintained, see <code>cargo-deps</code> <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-graph\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-graph.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-info\">cargo-info</a> — queries crates.io for crates details from command line <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/imp/cargo-info\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/imp/cargo-info.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-license\">cargo-license</a> — A cargo subcommand to quickly view the licenses of all dependencies. <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/onur/cargo-license\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/onur/cargo-license.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-make\">cargo-make</a> — Rust task runner and build tool. <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/sagiegurari/cargo-make\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/sagiegurari/cargo-make.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-modules\">cargo-modules</a> — A cargo plugin for showing a tree-like overview of a crate's modules. <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/regexident/cargo-modules\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/regexident/cargo-modules.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-multi\">cargo-multi</a> — runs specified cargo command on multiple crates <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/imp/cargo-multi\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/imp/cargo-multi.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-outdated\">cargo-outdated</a> — displays when newer versions of Rust dependencies are available, or out of date <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-outdated\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/kbknapp/cargo-outdated.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-release\">cargo-release</a> — tool for releasing git-managed cargo project, build, tag, publish, doc and push <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/sunng87/cargo-release\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/sunng87/cargo-release.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-script\">cargo-script</a> — lets people quickly and easily run Rust \"scripts\" which can make use of Cargo's package ecosystem <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/DanielKeep/cargo-script\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/DanielKeep/cargo-script.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-testify\">cargo-testify</a> — watches files changes, runs tests and notifies about the result with friendly OS notification <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/greyblake/cargo-testify\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/greyblake/cargo-testify.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sfackler/cargo-tree\">cargo-tree</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sfackler/cargo-tree\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">538</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":538,\"repo\":\"sfackler/cargo-tree\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> – Cargo subcommand that visualizes a crate's dependency graph in a tree-like format <a href=\"https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/sfackler/cargo-tree\"><img src=\"https://circleci.com/gh/sfackler/cargo-tree.svg?style=shield\" alt=\"CircleCI\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-update\">cargo-update</a> — cargo subcommand for checking and applying updates to installed executables <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/nabijaczleweli/cargo-update\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/nabijaczleweli/cargo-update.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://crates.io/crates/cargo-watch\">cargo-watch</a> — utility for cargo to compile projects when sources change <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/passcod/cargo-watch\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/passcod/cargo-watch.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/liuchong/cargo-x\">liuchong/cargo-x</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/liuchong/cargo-x\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":6,\"repo\":\"liuchong/cargo-x\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> — A very simple third-party cargo subcommand to execute a custom command <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/liuchong/cargo-x\"><img src=\"https://api.travis-ci.org/liuchong/cargo-x.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"build badge\"></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dtolnay/cargo-expand\">dtolnay/cargo-expand</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dtolnay/cargo-expand\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;f